		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Legendary</em></p><p><em>This tube holds a milky liquid with a strong alcohol smell. When found, a tube contains 1d6 + 1 ounces.</em></p><p><em>A magic item like this counts as magical for overcoming effects.</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong></p><ul><li><p>Pour 1 or more ounces onto a surface within reach. Each ounce instantly dissolves up to a 1-foot square of adhesive it touches, including @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-magic-items.Item.dmgSovereignGlue]{Sovereign Glue}.</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"foundry-secret-1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This item includes 7 limited uses. The <strong>Determine Ounces</strong> activity can be used to determine the number of ounces equivalent to 1d6 + 1.</p><p>The <strong>Apply Solvent</strong> activity allows you to select the number of ounces you're applying.</p></section>",
